title.narrative: 'Strengthened prevention and protection services to address child marriage and FGM/C

description.narrative: Following the launch of the National Costed Roadmap to end Child Marriage and FGM/C in August 2019, the Ministry of Women, Children and Youth (MoWCY), with support from UNICEF and UN Women, translated the roadmap into local languages, convened dialogues with regional bureaus, and initiated a partnership with national and local media to popularize action on the roadmap. It developed a briefing note including expected budget allocation, evidence-based strategies and interventions to be implemented which is being used in discussions officials are having with other sectors including health, education, justice and social protection. | Status:Met | As-of Date:24/08/2020
